<!-- FEATURE IMAGES -->
<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:85vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/1_20241021110701A092_20250609162243A215.jpg" alt="U5 PLUS Exterior"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Sleek Sedan Design</h3><p>The U5 PLUS features an excellent coefficient of drag for outstanding aerodynamics. Penetrating LED taillights with flow turn signals and LED daytime running lights on Honor trim create a striking visual presence.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side"><div class="feature-side-img"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/U5plus 2_20230213164138A125_20250609144743A172.jpg" alt="Interior"></div><div class="feature-side-content"><h3>Library-Class Quiet Cabin</h3><p>12.3-inch center screen paired with 7-inch and 12.3-inch LCD meters. Leather steering wheel with 2-way adjustment and multi-function controls. Manual anti-glare rearview mirror, dual sun visors with vanity mirrors, and front center armrest.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:80vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/3_20220927145230A050_20250609162335A219.jpg" alt="Dashboard"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Dual Powertrain Options</h3><p>1.5L engine with 83kW power and 142N&middot;m torque. Choose between 5MT manual or CVT automatic transmission. Front-wheel drive with MacPherson front and H torsion beam rear suspension. EPB electronic parking brake with Auto Hold standard.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/23/微信图片_20250623144012_20250623144230A405.webp" alt="Detail"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>Smart Safety</h4><p>ESP+TCS, ABS+EBD, EBA, HHC, TPMS standard. 360&deg; panoramic image on Honor trim.</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/5_20230616114250A213_20250609162259A216.jpg" alt="Comfort"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>Comfortable Space</h4><p>430L luggage volume with rear seat whole foldable. CN95 filter with pollen filtering A/C.</p></div></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side" style="direction:rtl"><div class="feature-side-img" style="direction:ltr"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2024/02/06/3_20240206100645A027.jpg" alt="Technology"></div><div class="feature-side-content" style="direction:ltr"><h3>Connected Intelligence</h3><p>BSD blind spot monitoring, LDW lane departure warning, and MOD low-speed dynamic object recognition on Honor. Bluetooth, radio, USB charging, and speed-sensing sound auto adjustment across all trims.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:70vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2022/08/11/7_20220811120353A073.jpg" alt="Rear"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Available in Four Colors</h3><p>Silver, Red, White, and Black body colors. Power sunroof standard on Honor, optional on Comfort. 16-inch aluminum alloy wheels with 205/55R16 tires.</p></div></section>

